{"tid":1535510,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益］跳左入閘","createTime":"2019-09-03T11:23:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T11:55:30.000Z","uid":288125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ca4e325d83dfc10ad867a6a38e0d42fd44a320a0","tid":1535510,"uid":288125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:23:23.000Z","msg":"有兩三個黑衫<br />\n得一個出閘位<br />\n點走成功率高啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc0572da48b0b341f375d786d91943b9bace1452","tid":1535510,"uid":290815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:23:49.000Z","msg":"其實要突破困局，依家只有「__」依個選項！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1534823\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1534823</a><br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：<br />\n香港民權抗爭&mdash;&mdash;五大訴求，缺一不可？我們需要更多！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530124\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530124</a>"},{"pid":"be45edae95e904863bf80d4d0656b68f629d9f6e","tid":1535510,"uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:24:58.000Z","msg":"練大隻<br />\n我今日show一show肌肉<br />\n班職員嚇到瀨尿<br />\n走都唔使走"},{"pid":"2f285d40a577f43467dc13357236e4d89d785d5b","tid":1535510,"uid":290815,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ca4e325d83dfc10ad867a6a38e0d42fd44a320a0","tid":1535510,"uid":288125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:23:23.000Z","msg":"有兩三個黑衫<br />\n得一個出閘位<br />\n點走成功率高啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:25:44.000Z","msg":"同職員講啱先有人跳閘，睇佢捉唔捉，唔捉就喺佢面前跳，捉就喺佢背後跳。"},{"pid":"7664509e4656a23ee8e1d629e3be697fcf302bda","tid":1535510,"uid":245499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:26:27.000Z","msg":"要睇係咩站<br />\n見冇黃衫 用入閘嗰邊跳 點睇?<br />\n有冇玻璃欄?"},{"pid":"2f5868e7f6d4a317e9c47440f75cfa091dfe1700","tid":1535510,"uid":45753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:29:51.000Z","msg":"唔好跳閘出去咪得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"debab51567f3274634ac6594f04a1cbda6174dc8","tid":1535510,"uid":143699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:42:03.000Z","msg":"大家真係冇需要再俾錢搭黨鐵啦，直接跳啦。大家唔好有任何嘅心理壓力，721，呢個月嘅封站，再加上太子站黨鐵嘅處理手法。佢唔再值得香港人俾一分一毫，我地一於全民跳閘<br />\n<br />\n1.呢隻係最簡單嘅跳法，肥啲都跳到，手腳並用，真係冇難度架，跳多兩次就會熟手。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Aimi1zO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAimi1zO.gif&h=e6d946f6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2.呢隻係新閘機，跳嘅時侯部機會響，要快手啲。同埋佢閘之間嘅距離有啲遠。用第一種跳法可能冇咁就手，建議直接跳過去，可以加個小助跑，都唔會太難。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iETUzUQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiETUzUQ.gif&h=c8f39564&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3. 呢種方法會比較安全。因為直接跳閘點都會有cctv影到，但係跳欄杆嘅話可以搵啲盲位／暗位，難啲發現。不過跳嘅難度會比較高。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tRMSmzS.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtRMSmzS.gif&h=73d4b461&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">同場加映錯誤示範</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MBkjO1B.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMBkjO1B.gif&h=c106dd4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢位狗狗好明顯冇睇教學片啦，大家千奇唔好學佢啊，動作要標準。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n注意事項：<br />\n－最好帶返口罩，遮一遮，保障返自已<br />\n－唔洗驚俾人捉到，就算俾人發現咗都可以直接跑走唔理佢，佢唔會真係追你9條街，當你離開咗佢個站嘅範圍，佢冇權捉你<br />\n－入閘時睇清楚有冇黃衫或可疑人士。真係得自已一個可以直接用第三招跳，最難捉。<br />\n－出閘嘅時侯更加唔洗驚，跳完係最近嘅出口快快手走人就得，唔會捉到你。<br />\n－其實仲有個安全啲嘅出閘方法，出閘果陣去客務到同佢講話岩岩係邊個邊個站嚟，但係跌咗張飛，問佢點算。你扮下野佢多數會俾一張一次性嘅綠色出閘卡你。我試過用呢招幾次都成功。<br />\n－黃衫人都係打份工，唔會同你咁搏命，都係果句，俾人捉到，大膽啲跑走唔好理佢<br />\n-最近黨鐵多咗狗，如果情況唔允許，希望大家都唔好勉強，可以改用老人卡。唔好因為咁而被人捉。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母狗鐵，你唔配收香港人錢呀。一齊跳佢老母閪！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n完整示範片段：\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pLjuuYOyhk8?list=LLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpLjuuYOyhk8%3Flist%3DLLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA&d=wLht58ApaBOsBOdSjqbSDfFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=a7584a37\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pLjuuYOyhk8?list=LLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA</a>"},{"pid":"c087734dffc04ba9e2b06fd7718ec96029c759b0","tid":1535510,"uid":159083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:50:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4d9af9b2cd24061993d56c39487be152f1a7b15","tid":1535510,"uid":288125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be45edae95e904863bf80d4d0656b68f629d9f6e","tid":1535510,"uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:24:58.000Z","msg":"練大隻<br />\n我今日show一show肌肉<br />\n班職員嚇到瀨尿<br />\n走都唔使走"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:50:53.000Z","msg":"肌到用時方恨少⋯"},{"pid":"cbfc970636f49f1c5a45bb9fceca2ddbc6ec82c4","tid":1535510,"uid":288125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7664509e4656a23ee8e1d629e3be697fcf302bda","tid":1535510,"uid":245499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:26:27.000Z","msg":"要睇係咩站<br />\n見冇黃衫 用入閘嗰邊跳 點睇?<br />\n有冇玻璃欄?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:55:30.000Z","msg":"e.g 海怡<br />\n出入都係同一邊<br />\n仲未有信心過玻璃欄..."}]}